</ol>
<p local-id=3D"e6f6f44c26c5" style=3D"margin-left: 30.0px;">1.1 SignIn_Shou=
ldReturnNull_WhenUserDoesNotExist<br>
 Null-t ad vissza, ha a felhaszn=C3=A1l=C3=B3 nem l=C3=A9tezik az adatb=C3=
=A1zisban.</p>
<p local-id=3D"e82d39193c28" style=3D"margin-left: 30.0px;">1.2 SignIn_Shou=
ldReturnNull_WhenPasswordIsIncorrect<br>
 Null-t ad vissza, ha a jelsz=C3=B3 helytelen.</p>
<p local-id=3D"74e7cf5ab55a" style=3D"margin-left: 30.0px;">1.3 SignIn_Shou=
ldReturnTokens_WhenCredentialsAreValid<br>
 Sikeres bejelentkez=C3=A9s eset=C3=A9n access =C3=A9s refresh tokeneket ad=
 vissza.<br>
 Ellen=C5=91rzi, hogy mindk=C3=A9t token nem null =C3=A9s nem =C3=BCres.</p=
>
<p local-id=3D"e02e2c22fd09" style=3D"margin-left: 30.0px;">1.4 SignIn_Shou=
ldSaveRefreshToken_WhenLoginSucceeds<br>
 Sikeres bejelentkez=C3=A9s ut=C3=A1n a refresh token ment=C3=A9sre ker=C3=
=BCl az<br>
 adatb=C3=A1zisba, a lej=C3=A1rati id=C5=91 j=C3=B6v=C5=91beli d=C3=A1tumra=
 van =C3=A1ll=C3=ADtva.</p>
<p local-id=3D"20e06bd370a0" style=3D"margin-left: 30.0px;">1.5 RefreshToke=
ns_ShouldReturnNewTokens_WhenTokensAreValid<br>
 =C3=89rv=C3=A9nyes tokenekkel t=C3=B6rt=C3=A9n=C5=91 friss=C3=ADt=C3=A9s e=
set=C3=A9n =C3=BAj access =C3=A9s refresh<br>
 tokeneket ad vissza.</p>
<p local-id=3D"43344bfc5e9d" style=3D"margin-left: 30.0px;">1.6 RefreshToke=
ns_ShouldReturnNull_WhenRefreshTokenIsInvalid<br>
 Null-t ad vissza, ha a refresh token =C3=A9rv=C3=A9nytelen (manipul=C3=A1l=
t).</p>
<p local-id=3D"646546e48b54" style=3D"margin-left: 30.0px;">1.7 RefreshToke=
ns_ShouldReturnNull_WhenAccessTokenIsInvalid<br>
 Null-t ad vissza, ha az access token =C3=A9rv=C3=A9nytelen (nem val=C3=B3s=
 JWT).</p>
<p local-id=3D"d38e2f51db64"></p>
<ol start=3D"2" local-id=3D"7593d727bb82">
<li local-id=3D"03c5bca49c5d">
